divs: sighting detailstaking pictures of storm clouds,these were not visable until i downloaded the pics,guess you never know what may show up!finally got decent pictures,zoom into the right on the 1st pic,the second is pretty clear... the next night my wife,daughter & i watched the sky-saw 7 total unexplained lights high up-it looked like they were going to a meeting!one was close though-bright star\diamond like 30?degree on horizon,sat for 4-5 secs & blinked out,guess they were letting us know they were here too.i'm from the k.c. area & have had multiple sighting there since april,one as close as 25' from me,orange orb,beachball size-looked like an eye closing when it blinked out.anyway enjoy the pics!! oh-forgot to mention the birdlike ufo-call me on that one.
